The Chi-Mek delivery is here.
(chicken and beer)

293
00:23:31,130 --> 00:23:33,410
What are you doing in the dark?

294
00:23:33,410 --> 00:23:35,270
How did you know to come here?

295
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:37,680
Your mother called me.

296
00:23:41,290 --> 00:23:43,480
What are you still doing here?

297
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:45,120
Let's go home now.

298
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:47,190
I don't want to.

299
00:23:50,730 --> 00:23:55,360
So?  Where is this Do Min Joon that
 you're sitting around waiting for?

300
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:59,830
When is he coming back?  No, why did he go?

301
