308
00:24:30,090 --> 00:24:32,720
I couldn't do anything for him.

309
00:24:34,130 --> 00:24:37,350
And I couldn't even say a proper goodbye.

310
00:24:39,590 --> 00:24:42,710
Even there, he's going to do everything that he can.

311
00:24:43,910 --> 00:24:46,660
