313
00:24:53,350 --> 00:24:56,320
And even though at the end, he might not be able to return,

314
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:02,170
I won't forget.

315
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:05,720
I won't forget a single thing,

316
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:09,840
