319
00:25:23,590 --> 00:25:25,220
A favour?

320
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:31,780
 In a little while,

321
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:35,990
 I might have to go somewhere.

322
00:25:37,150 --> 00:25:39,840
 If Cheon Song Yi ends up alone,

323
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:44,690
 I'm most worried about you.

324
00:25:45,930 --> 00:25:49,730
 But, at the same time, I'm most comforted by you, too.

325
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:54,450
