332
00:26:12,320 --> 00:26:15,120
 I'll take care of that on my own, too.

333
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:19,430
 As you do it your way,
I'll protect Cheon Song Yi my own way.

334
00:26:27,340 --> 00:26:29,250
Really?

335
00:26:30,390 --> 00:26:32,360
That's what he said?

336
00:26:32,360 --> 00:26:35,200
Yeah, so eat.

337
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:37,900
Your mother is really worried.

338
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:41,710
I bought porridge, too. 
Do you want to eat it first?

339
