351
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:49,080
Yes, and she ate some porridge.

352
00:27:49,080 --> 00:27:52,080
Yes, don't worry.

353
00:27:52,860 --> 00:27:54,480
Yes.

354
00:28:04,620 --> 00:28:06,690
Rotten jerk.

355
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:13,700
What are you doing?
This is Do Min Joon's. Why do you have it?

356
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:15,190
Min Joon hyung gave it to me.

357
00:28:15,190 --> 00:28:18,410
This?  To you?  Why?

358
00:28:20,410 --> 00:28:23,560
 Hyung, why did you call me here?

359
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:25,790
 Oh.

360
00:28:26,620 --> 00:28:30,420
 I'll be going on a trip.

361
00:28:31,870 --> 00:28:36,430
- Is it the kind of trip that I'm thinking of?
-Hmm?

