00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:52,420
 In any case, I think it might be a slightly lengthy trip.

365
00:28:53,230 --> 00:28:55,660
 So, I wanted to ask you for a favor.

366
00:28:56,330 --> 00:28:59,760
 Yes, please say it. Whatever it is.

367
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:04,330
 While I'm gone, listen well to your sister.

368
00:29:04,330 --> 00:29:06,510
 And, don't upset your sister.

369
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:09,040
 And, just do whatever she tells you to.

370
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:12,740
 That's well . . . Even though it's you asking that of me ...

371
00:29:12,740 --> 00:29:15,190
 The telescopes . . .

372
00:29:17,290 --> 00:29:20,220
 Didn't you say you wanted them?

373
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,640
 I'll give them to you.

374
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,830
 Both of them?

375
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:27,570
 Both of them.

376
00:29:28,190 --> 00:29:30,660
 If Noona tells me to die, I will.

377
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:31,980
 Okay.

378
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:38,690
 Don't make things difficult for your sister,
and stay by her side, dependably taking care of her.

379
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,960
 Thanks, Hyung.

