00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:51,100
He told every punk out there to take care of me.

384
00:29:51,100 --> 00:29:54,780
But, when does Min Joon hyung's trip end?

385
00:29:54,780 --> 00:29:56,820
Where did he go?

386
00:30:09,350 --> 00:30:13,190
Cheon Song Yi's phone is turned off today, too.

387
00:30:13,950 --> 00:30:15,550
What is this?!

388
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:18,590
We already gave her two weeks for personal reasons!

389
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:23,530
I thought things were getting better,
 but I see that her old habits are coming out again.

390
00:30:23,530 --> 00:30:26,160
I should just fire her!

391
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:28,110
Just a minute.

392
00:30:28,110 --> 00:30:29,800
Ow! My head!

393
00:30:30,760 --> 00:30:33,140
Director,

394
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:34,960
Are you going to fire Song Yi?

395
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,670
Huh?

396
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:40,120
You have thought really well.

397
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:44,460
Anyway, there are a lot of articles here and there about waiting for Cheon Song Yi. . .

