00:30:53,290 --> 00:30:56,540
Why don't you cut her out completely this time?

402
00:30:56,540 --> 00:31:00,680
With me alone, we could probably be successful somehow.

403
00:31:00,680 --> 00:31:03,620
Could it possibly be ruined?

404
00:31:04,130 --> 00:31:07,120
No, I'm not saying I'm firing her.

