00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:09,680
It's just I would want to.

406
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:13,190
Miss Se Mi, can't you get in touch with Song Yi?
You're friends, right?

407
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:15,260
We're not close.

