00:31:17,290 --> 00:31:19,540
How should I do it?

409
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:20,930
Please cut it short.

410
00:31:20,930 --> 00:31:22,730
Shorter than this?!

411
00:31:22,730 --> 00:31:25,430
In cutting  my hair,

412
00:31:25,430 --> 00:31:27,570
I want to cut off all the regrets too.

