00:31:27,570 --> 00:31:29,350
Another man?

414
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:31,600
Why did you break up this time?

415
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:36,630
In my own way, he was a man I played hard to get.

416
00:31:36,970 --> 00:31:41,530
Although... there wasn't any pulling, but rather
 he just pushed pushed pushed.

417
00:31:41,530 --> 00:31:42,770
But then?

418
00:31:42,770 --> 00:31:46,590
--With my trusted friend. . .
--Oh my god!

