00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:30,460
Your hair makes half of your image.

434
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:33,050
You can't.

435
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:45,850
Hey, is it that funny?

436
00:32:46,850 --> 00:32:50,590
It's so funny!
"I'm not buying."

