00:33:25,410 --> 00:33:27,530
Are you crying?

448
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:43,250
Bok Ja, it's been a long time.

449
00:33:43,250 --> 00:33:45,630
I changed my name ten years ago.

450
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:48,990
Call me Hae In, please

451
00:33:50,370 --> 00:33:52,110
What's wrong with her?

452
00:33:52,110 --> 00:33:54,670
Because of Do Min Joon.

453
00:33:56,940 --> 00:34:01,670
Hey, Cheon Song Yi, the director said he will fire you 
if you don't come tomorrow.

454
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:08,140
