00:34:12,140 --> 00:34:14,320
Don't you have one?

457
00:34:14,320 --> 00:34:18,070
You also met Do Min Joon, right?

458
00:34:18,750 --> 00:34:21,820
Did anything interesting happen?

459
00:34:21,820 --> 00:34:25,170
Any kind of story is fine,

460
00:34:25,170 --> 00:34:28,760
so say anything.
Please?

461
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:38,610
Do Min Joon.

462
00:34:39,930 --> 00:34:42,850
Come to my room.

463
00:34:44,020 --> 00:34:49,470

464
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:52,350
What are you doing?

465
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:56,670
Just.

466
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:01,410
Are you really Cheon Song Yi?

467
00:35:03,930 --> 00:35:06,810
How long will it take?

468
00:35:06,810 --> 00:35:09,660
For it not to be painful when I hear stories about him,

469
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:12,450
how long will it take?

470
00:35:12,450 --> 00:35:15,020
Will that day even come?

471
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:17,670
When you start to think about him,

472
00:35:17,670 --> 00:35:19,930
that's when it isn't going to hurt.

473
00:35:21,090 --> 00:35:22,490
What are you saying?

474
00:35:22,490 --> 00:35:26,940
