475
00:35:26,940 --> 00:35:30,080
There is no time when you are not thinking of him.

476
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:34,720
Not thinking is harder.

477
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:40,880
But then, when it's time, you will suddenly  
think of that person.

478
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:47,330
"Ahh. . . I was thinking of something else, 
but then now I'm thinking of that person."

479
00:35:48,340 --> 00:35:51,140
