 some kind of pro at this.

482
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:02,570
How long did it take?

483
00:36:03,020 --> 00:36:04,990
15 years.

484
00:36:04,990 --> 00:36:07,030
Are you kidding me?

485
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:09,850
