00:36:41,530 --> 00:36:43,620
What Se Mi said was right.

491
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:46,580
It's harder now not to think of him than

492
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:50,460
it is to think of him.

493
00:36:52,620 --> 00:36:54,500
That's why,

494
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:58,750
 I go alone to the places that we went to together.

495
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:01,660
 Reflect and . . .

496
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:05,060
 long for him and . . .

497
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:10,160
 look for traces of him.

498
00:37:16,530 --> 00:37:19,060
 I'm waiting for that person.

499
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:23,720
And, also that day has come.

500
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:27,470
The day that we promised, 100th day.

501
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:32,570
The appointed place, the Namsan Tower.

502
00:37:32,570 --> 00:37:38,230

503
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:29,780
 ♫ Eventually,

504
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:36,500
♫  I recognized you in a glance

505
00:38:37,220 --> 00:38:42,150
 ♫ Everything was obviously different.

506
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:50,110
 ♫ My world was divided between before and after knowing you.

507
00:38:50,980 --> 00:38:57,920
♫  When you breathe, a warm breeze blows.

508
00:38:57,920 --> 00:39:05,430
♫  When you smile, a dazzling sun shines.

509
00:39:12,230 --> 00:39:14,610
I think it was about that time.

510
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:20,500
I used to think I was mistaken,
but it felt like I really did see him.

511
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:23,930
No, I did see that person, Do Min Joon.

512
00:39:23,930 --> 00:39:26,730
But this doesn't make sense.

513
00:39:27,420 --> 00:39:30,570
Am I slowly going crazy?

514
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:35,590
It's the same for me as well.

515
00:39:35,590 --> 00:39:40,440
I don't know what's going on with my mind.  The last time...

516
00:39:47,470 --> 00:39:50,520
 It must be all good now.

517
00:39:51,870 --> 00:39:54,630
 This also relieves my heart.

518
00:39:54,630 --> 00:39:57,050
 Lawyer Jang.

519
00:39:57,050 --> 00:39:58,600
 Yes!

520
00:40:00,230 --> 00:40:02,490
 Teacher!

521
00:40:13,480 --> 00:40:15,930
It was so strange that I went to the hospital.

522
00:40:15,930 --> 00:40:21,400
They said I was out of touch with reality 
as a reaction to acute stress.

523
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:23,910
Having someone go to a place where
you can no longer see them,

524
00:40:23,910 --> 00:40:28,450
is the same as the stress when someone you love dies.

525
